'''Papal Arbitration''' was a form of [[international arbitration]] used between warring [[Roman Catholic]] countries where the [[Pope]] tried to bring both sides to peace.<ref>{{CathEncy|wstitle=Papal Arbitration}}</ref>  A recent example was the [[Papal mediation in the Beagle conflict]] between [[Argentina]] and [[Chile]].

